85
00:06:12,250 --> 00:06:14,460
to charge without their commander?

86
00:06:15,460 --> 00:06:16,920
Ah, that's right.

87
00:06:17,130 --> 00:06:19,510
You're the only one who stayed behind.

88
00:06:19,590 --> 00:06:22,380
