102
00:07:07,430 --> 00:07:09,010
It's Delphyne's army.

103
00:07:09,310 --> 00:07:11,430
They are coming straight this way.

104
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,140
Huh?

105
00:07:17,150 --> 00:07:20,570
Without a doubt they want
to kill you Lady Komari.

106
00:07:20,900 --> 00:07:23,110
I feel the desire for revenge.

107
00:07:23,190 --> 00:07:25,780
Why?
What did I do?

108
00:07:26,110 --> 00:07:27,570
At the meeting of The Seven

109
00:07:27,910 --> 00:07:31,240
everyone thinks you were
the one who killed Lord Delphyne.

110
00:07:31,330 --> 00:07:32,290
All false charges!

111
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:36,540
We need to go Lady Komari.
If we stay here we'll die.

112
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:38,460
I want to go home.

113
00:07:44,170 --> 00:07:46,510
Lady Komari, you shouldn't touch me there.

114
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:49,760
Just shut it!
Hurry up and go, you perverted maid!

115
00:07:51,180 --> 00:07:52,890
Commander Terakomari has

116
00:07:52,970 --> 00:07:55,180
sent her whole force at Commander Frête,

117
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:58,350
leaving her a single horse
against Delphyne's army.

118
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:01,070
Now, in the midst of the chaos,

119
00:08:01,150 --> 00:08:03,230
the 6th Corps has yet to make a move.

120
00:08:03,530 --> 00:08:07,700
