Sakuna Memoir is the culprit

138
00:09:05,170 --> 00:09:07,210
murdering government officials.

139
00:09:07,510 --> 00:09:09,430
-We'll capture he--
-Just hold on.

140
00:09:10,260 --> 00:09:13,800
If we intervene now,
all we'll get is the lizard's tail.

141
00:09:14,430 --> 00:09:18,520
