Vill!

247
00:16:44,420 --> 00:16:45,970
Where are you?

248
00:16:47,470 --> 00:16:49,010
Vill!

249
00:16:51,510 --> 00:16:54,600
Good, she's still alive.

250
00:16:55,850 --> 00:16:57,230
Thank you.

251
00:16:57,310 --> 00:17:00,350
