259
00:17:28,470 --> 00:17:30,050
Are you alone?

260
00:17:31,140 --> 00:17:32,600
Alone?

261
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:35,390
Yes, that's right!

262
00:17:35,600 --> 00:17:38,600
You massacred everyone!

263
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:39,690
Huh?

264
00:17:39,850 --> 00:17:41,270
Lord Heaven, Lord Metal,

265
00:17:41,350 --> 00:17:43,270
Lord Memoir, and Delphyne!

266
00:17:43,810 --> 00:17:45,020
What are you saying?

267
00:17:45,110 --> 00:17:46,280
