00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:51,070
There's no way you're able to use

270
00:17:51,160 --> 00:17:53,160
magic with such destructive power!

271
00:17:53,450 --> 00:17:54,990
I'm telling you...

272
00:17:59,500 --> 00:18:01,500
Is that the ruby?

273
00:18:01,790 --> 00:18:02,750
You can't have!

274
00:18:03,500 --> 00:18:06,000
It's not what you think,
I didn't break it!

275
00:18:06,090 --> 00:18:07,710
You've got to be kidding!

276
00:18:08,010 --> 00:18:09,760
You only want to save yourself

277
00:18:09,840 --> 00:18:11,470
so you break the ruby

278
00:18:11,550 --> 00:18:13,590
and try to ruin the clash!

279
00:18:13,680 --> 00:18:14,890
No, that's wrong!

280
00:18:15,180 --> 00:18:18,390
By the time I came to it was destroyed!

281
00:18:18,970 --> 00:18:21,640
You are a cancer to the empire!

282
00:18:21,940 --> 00:18:25,770
I refuse to let you go around
doing as you please anymore!

283
00:18:29,740 --> 00:18:31,650
I don't want to be killed!

284
00:18:31,740 --> 00:18:33,820
Then fight back like a warrior would!

285
00:18:37,700 --> 00:18:38,830
Dark Magic...

286
00:18:39,910 --> 00:18:41,620
"Darkness Arma--"

287
00:19:15,450 --> 00:19:17,120
Thank goodness.

288
00:19:17,700 --> 00:19:19,740
I finally found you.

289
00:19:21,290 --> 00:19:22,710
Y-Yeah.

290
00:19:23,290 --> 00:19:25,370
I'm glad you're safe, Sakuna.

291
00:19:25,880 --> 00:19:27,290
Though...

292
00:19:27,750 --> 00:19:30,170
Sakuna, have you...

293
00:19:30,550 --> 00:19:32,510
Have you always been that strong?

294
00:19:32,590 --> 00:19:34,090
I'm not strong.

295
00:19:34,430 --> 00:19:36,470
Ms. Frête let her guard down.

296
00:19:37,180 --> 00:19:40,390
But Sakuna, you are a sorceress right?

297
00:19:40,810 --> 00:19:43,480
You punched through her
with your bare hand.

298
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:45,390
You're able to do that?

299
00:19:45,730 --> 00:19:47,310
Anyone can do that.

300
00:19:47,610 --> 00:19:49,360
At least a normal vampire.

301
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:50,520
I-I see.

302
00:19:50,940 --> 00:19:51,940
Right.

303
00:19:52,570 --> 00:19:55,610
Now almost all of The Seven have died.

304
00:20:11,550 --> 00:20:13,130
Do you remember?

305
00:20:13,840 --> 00:20:14,720
Huh?

306
00:20:15,090 --> 00:20:17,300
The night we watched the stars together.

307
00:20:17,390 --> 00:20:20,430
The question that I asked you.

308
00:20:24,890 --> 00:20:26,890
That's when you said

309
00:20:27,310 --> 00:20:31,070
you would defeat
the terrorist threatening you.

310
00:20:32,020 --> 00:20:34,440
I thought that was amazing.

311
00:20:35,280 --> 00:20:36,780
Sakuna...

312
00:20:37,450 --> 00:20:39,240
Looking at everything,

313
00:20:39,660 --> 00:20:42,740
I realize your words were
not pretentious or vain

314
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:46,410
but it was really you speaking the truth.

315
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:49,750
What are you saying?

316
00:20:50,210 --> 00:20:52,590
But I can't be like you.

317
00:20:53,090 --> 00:20:54,670
With my lack of strength

318
00:20:54,760 --> 00:20:56,760
I'm no match for the Inverted Moons.

319
00:20:57,300 --> 00:20:58,970
No matter how hard I try,

320
00:20:59,050 --> 00:21:01,140
no matter how loyal I am to them,

321
00:21:01,220 --> 00:21:03,850
no matter how much I beg them to stop

322
00:21:03,930 --> 00:21:07,270
they'll still kill the people that I love.

323
00:21:07,770 --> 00:21:10,350
There was nothing that I could do.

324
00:21:10,560 --> 00:21:12,980
Because I don't have strength or courage.

325
00:21:13,070 --> 00:21:15,280
Because I don't want to be killed.

326
00:21:16,610 --> 00:21:19,240
I only have one choice.

327
00:21:19,950 --> 00:21:21,870
I always have and I always will

328
00:21:22,620 --> 00:21:26,000
have to work hard as
one of the cogs of the Inverted Moons.

329
00:21:29,040 --> 00:21:30,620
Ms. Frête also

330
00:21:30,710 --> 00:21:33,130
doesn't know where the magic cores are.

331
00:21:38,720 --> 00:21:41,180
Ms. Terakomari, I'm so sorry.

332
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:43,600
The terrorist...

333
00:21:44,060 --> 00:21:45,770
was me all along.

334
00:21:47,020 --> 00:21:48,020
Sakuna...

335
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:49,980
Are you crying?

336
00:21:50,100 --> 00:21:51,520
Are you hurt somewhere?

337
00:21:51,600 --> 00:21:54,690
Why are you worried about me?

338
00:21:54,900 --> 00:21:57,820
I'm a terrorist of the Inverted Moons!

339
00:21:57,900 --> 00:21:59,030
Stop joking around!

340
00:21:59,450 --> 00:22:01,990
If you are crying then
let's go home together.

341
00:22:03,620 --> 00:22:05,910
Even if I want to go home I can't.

342
00:22:07,540 --> 00:22:10,540
I wanted you to
know the truth, Ms. Terakomari.

343
00:22:11,580 --> 00:22:14,500
It would be unfortunate to
have to kill each other

344
00:22:14,590 --> 00:22:16,550
without knowing.

345
00:22:17,460 --> 00:22:18,920
Mental Magic

346
00:22:19,630 --> 00:22:21,180
"Mind Refrain."

347
00:23:57,270 --> 00:23:59,480
Rotating Asterism

